arStrings.szText: You can now earn {c_highlight}Midwinter Nightmare Caches{/c} containing assortments of event materials by completing {icon:nightmare_dungeon, 2.5}{c_highlight}Nightmare Dungeons (Unlocked in WT3){/c}.
The {icon:hibernal_ward, 2.5}{c_highlight}Midwinter Ward{/c} stands ready to empower your battle against the Red-Cloaked Horror and its Blightfiends.
Continue earning {icon:hibernal_proofs, 2.5}{c_highlight}Midwinter Proofs{/c} to purchase all the exciting {c_highlight}limited-time{/c} rewards Gileon has to offer before The Midwinter Blight ends!
